headline: The CHIPS AHOY! Brand Serves Up Fan Fun with the CHIPS AHOY! Cookie x Stranger Things Claw Machine Giveaway
summary: This October, the CHIPS AHOY! Brand is joining forces with Stranger Things in a deliciously eerie way, letting both cookie and show enthusiasts experience the brands IRL. On Saturday, October 25, just days before Halloween, fans in New York City and Atlanta can get a taste of the Upside Down with a pop-up experience full of retro thrills, exclusive prizes* and a cookie that's anything but ordinary (while supplies last).
